      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver with character? This car is in fair condition and has been a reliable companion through many journeys. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking affordable and steady transportation. It's ready to hit the road with its next owner today!",
