    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owner. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and is ready for daily use without any immediate repair needs. The exterior is clean, though it does show some minor cosmetic blemishes and light scratches expected with its age, and the interior is well-kept with only minimal signs of wear. It represents a reliable option for anyone looking for a solid, pre-owned car.",
