    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The engine and transmission are functional and the car drives well, but you should expect some minor oil seepage and a suspension that feels a bit loose on rough roads. Visually, the exterior has several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and the interior upholstery shows significant wear and some staining. It is a solid choice for someone who prioritizes mechanical function over aesthetics or is willing to put in a little work to freshen it up.",
