    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s been really well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and drives like a dream! It\u2019s been perfect for me, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. It's clean, runs smoothly, and is ready to hit the road for many more adventures. If you're looking for a solid car that won't let you down, you've found it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
