    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained and reliable vehicle that perfectly balances performance with everyday practicality. The exterior finish retains a high-quality luster, showing only minor, superficial stone chips consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the seats remain supportive and comfortable with no tears or heavy bolsters wear, and all interior electronics\u2014including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control\u2014function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision, backed by a comprehensive service record that proves its mechanical integrity. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car has been smoke-free and garage-kept, offering a tight, rattle-free driving experience that feels solid on both city streets and highways. It is a complete package for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-functioning vehicle without the premium price tag of a showroom-new model.",
